---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<section id="cobertura" class="relative py-28 lg:py-40 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-surface dark:bg-surface-dark" />
  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 lg:mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
        Cobertura <span class="text-brand">Nacional</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted dark:text-muted-dark max-w-[55ch] mx-auto">
        Entregamos en todo el país desde nuestra base en San Cristóbal. Llegamos directo a tu obra o proyecto.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <div class="p-1.5 rounded-[2rem] bg-border dark:bg-border-dark">
          <div class="rounded-[calc(2rem-0.375rem)] overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-8 lg:p-12">
            <div class="relative aspect-[16/9] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
              <img src={`${base}images/dump-truck.jpg`} alt="Cobertura nacional" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent" />
              <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 text-white">
                <div class="font-bold text-xl">Cobertura nacional</div>
                <p class="text-sm text-white/80">Base principal: San Cristóbal, RD</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=San+Cristobal+Republica+Dominicana" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-border dark:border-border-dark hover:border-brand/30 transition-all group">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-brand/20 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-1">San Cristóbal</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">Base principal y punto de carga — Ver en Google Maps</p>
        </a>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-border dark:border-border-dark">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 9V5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 10.5 3h6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25v13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 16.5 21h-6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V15m-3 0-3-3m0 0 3-3m-3 3H15" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-1">Entregas a domicilio</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">Directo a tu obra o proyecto</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-border dark:border-border-dark">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-1">Horario flexible</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">Coordinamos la entrega según tu necesidad</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
